    "course_title": "INTRODUCTORY APPLIED STATISTICS FOR ENGINEERS",
    "description": "Descriptive statistics, probability concepts and distributions, random variables. Hypothesis tests and confidence intervals for one- and two-sample problems. Linear regression, model checking, and inference. Analysis of variance and basic ideas in experimental design. Utilizes the R programming language.",
